You can find this tiny place amongst the wide selection of other restaurants, but I can assure you none of them will leave you as satisfied as Very Crepe. Their crepes are not only exquisitely delicious (and quite big as well), but the prices are some of the best you’ll see in a city such as Sunny Isles Beach. If you’re craving something more oriental, they also have an incredible selection of poke bowls. Not only that, but their smoothies are some of the best smoothies I’ve tried in a while. Completely natural and no added sugar, they’re so fresh! Staff is super nice as well.

We had the Russian and the NY pastrami and the dessert one with bananas, blueberries, strawberries, Nutella and whipped cream. It was a beautiful experience!! The Machiado was perfect too!! If you like crepes you wil LOVE stopping here!! ❤️❤️😊
